{{-- Reusable "compare Youform to other tools" link block. Passes internal-link authority from
     hub pages (survey builder, survey templates) down to the competitor-alternative pages.
     Keyword-rich anchors ("<Competitor> alternative") reinforce each page's ranking target.
     Self-contained, no params (avoids Jigsaw __isset gotcha). Include before partials.footer. --}}
<div class="bg-medium-champagne py-16 border-t-2 border-black">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-10 md:px-20 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-3">See how Youform compares to other survey tools</h2>
        <p class="text-base text-gray-700 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            Switching from another tool? See how Youform stacks up on price, features, and unlimited responses.
        </p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
            <a href="/typeform-alternative/" class="flex items-center justify-center px-5 py-4 bg-white border-2 border-black rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-aquamarine transition-colors">Typeform alternative</a>
            <a href="/surveymonkey-alternative/" class="flex items-center justify-center px-5 py-4 bg-white border-2 border-black rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-aquamarine transition-colors">SurveyMonkey alternative</a>
            <a href="/qualtrics-alternative/" class="flex items-center justify-center px-5 py-4 bg-white border-2 border-black rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-aquamarine transition-colors">Qualtrics alternative</a>
            <a href="/jotform-alternative/" class="flex items-center justify-center px-5 py-4 bg-white border-2 border-black rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-aquamarine transition-colors">Jotform alternative</a>
            <a href="/tally-forms-alternative/" class="flex items-center justify-center px-5 py-4 bg-white border-2 border-black rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-aquamarine transition-colors">Tally Forms alternative</a>
            <a href="/fillout-alternative/" class="flex items-center justify-center px-5 py-4 bg-white border-2 border-black rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-aquamarine transition-colors">Fillout alternative</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
